We don't want to directly consider the most frequent next activity, so we will look for the next activity immediately following the last of the prefix in the matching trace. Since the matching trace has four events, the next activity would be the fifth event, which is "end trip".

The final answer is: $\boxed{end trip}$
Expected Answer: Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER
Verification Result: False
